2007-01-03  Christian Persch  <chpe@svn.gnome.org>

	* Makefile.am:
	* configure.in:
	* glade-3.desktop.in.in:
	* po/POTFILES.in:
	* po/POTFILES.skip:
	Add version to bugzilla info in the .desktop file. Bug #392395.

